ZH: 我们站在看台上观看比赛。
EN: We stood on the stands to watch the game.

ZH: 看台上挤满了观众。
EN: The stands were packed with spectators.

ZH: 看台的灯光很亮。
EN: The lights on the stands were very bright.

ZH: 这个看台可以容纳上千人。
EN: This stand can accommodate over a thousand people.

ZH: 我们在看台上等待演出的开始。
EN: We waited on the stands for the performance to begin.

ZH: 看台上的座位都很舒服。
EN: The seats on the stands are all very comfortable.

ZH: 看台上有很多摄影师在工作。
EN: There are many photographers working on the stands.

ZH: 球迷们在看台上大声欢呼。
EN: The fans cheered loudly on the stands.

ZH: 我们在看台上看到了名人。
EN: We saw celebrities on the stands.

ZH: 观众们都争先恐后地站在看台上。
EN: The audience rushed to stand on the stands.

ZH: 球场上的看台建得非常坚固。
EN: The stands at the stadium are built very sturdy.

ZH: 看台上挂着许多彩旗。
EN: Many colorful flags are hanging on the stands.

ZH: 看台上的气氛非常热烈。
EN: The atmosphere on the stands is very lively.

ZH: 看台顶部有一个巨大的告示牌。
EN: There is a huge billboard at the top of the stands.

ZH: 我们在看台上看到了远处的景色。
EN: We saw the view in the distance from the stands.

ZH: 看台上的演出非常精彩。
EN: The performance on the stands was very exciting.

ZH: 我们站在看台上看到了全场的人群。
EN: We stood on the stands and saw the crowd in the whole stadium.

ZH: 球员们在比赛结束后向看台致意。
EN: The players saluted the stands after the game.

ZH: 看台下是一片绿茵场。
EN: Below the stands is a green field.

ZH: 观众们在看台上起立鼓掌。
EN: The audience stood and applauded on the stands.
